okButtonAction

protected boolean okButtonAction()
Does all the things necessary when user pushes OK button and returns true if there was nothing rejected. Returning false means the regular OK button action has not been done to the end, e.g. because data input has not been accepted.

Returns:
true if there was nothing rejected
